ir人就有一Pair<br />\n未必係你做得特別差嘅<br />\n佢個心唔喺你度，唔離都冇意思"},{"pid":"3d9787e6fd6b2ca035e3b4f512d7f23609e38a89","tid":681622,"uid":80966,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89252d5974b87946818bfcbe465dddf4ddfe04a9","tid":681622,"uid":91767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人突然唔鐘意你 其實即係鐘意左其他人<br />\n復合到都分分鐘已經同第二個男人搞過<br />\n咁仲有咩意思<br />\n真話往往係最難聽<br />\n早日放下啦巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人係唔會突然間唔中意一個人。其實佢之前一早已經唔鍾意樓主，只不過佢未識到第二個男人所以提出離婚。而家既有咗第二個男人梗係提出啦。"},{"pid":"ea36d1ccaa25bbd872d2968c352dccf88f188b57","tid":681622,"uid":79943,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3d9787e6fd6b2ca035e3b4f512d7f23609e38a89","tid":681622,"uid":80966,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"咁老實講我都知佢有外遇，只係我唔明點解佢要結婚，結婚仲要搞呢啲嘢，為咩？"},{"pid":"d23001f3b10975fa36e6dd6272362409fe761c7d","tid":681622,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea36d1ccaa25bbd872d2968c352dccf88f188b57","tid":681622,"uid":79943,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3d9787e6fd6b2ca035e3b4f512d7f23609e38a89","tid":681622,"uid":80966,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"咁老實講我都知佢有外遇，只係我唔明點解佢要結婚，結婚仲要搞呢啲嘢，為咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"為身家"},{"pid":"facb2b2b45b0f7dded08d203935a058a4e4502b2","tid":681622,"uid":24432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"放手啦，由佢變心個一刻<br />\n當日你愛既個一個佢已經死左<br />\n你留得住個人，都唔會留得到佢個心"},{"pid":"c7a887b412455055d8dd15006eacc56b4398b988","tid":681622,"uid":79943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d23001f3b10975fa36e6dd6272362409fe761c7d","tid":681622,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"